LENX Professional 20 PCS Gundam Modeler Basic Tools Craft Set For Car Model Assemble Building 

The modeler basic tools set is suitable for a beginner and advanced modeler as well.

Package include :
2 X Screwdriver;
5 X Files; 
1 X Separator;
1 X Steel rule;
3 X Polishing Block; 
5 X Tweezers;
1 X Graver and 1 Box Blade;
1 X Diagonal Pliers.

Note:
Because the Modeler Basic Tools are very shape, please use with care and take they away from children.
